originalText.text:
I have had several sessions with walter and can’t believe the results I’m experiencing. I came to walter with a lot of tension throughout my whole body from long term emotional trauma as well as physical from a car accident I was in years ago. I have tried many different modalities but none of them had long lasting results or the deep release I’ve been looking for.  CST from Walter has changed my life and body. I feel so much more comfortable in my body and deal with a significant less amount of pain on a daily basis... which I think will eventually completely go away with more seasons!

I am a classical singer and have noticed a huge difference in my sound and support since seeing Walter.

Every time I leave a session not only do I feel physically free, but I notice my mood is greatly elevated.

Walter is very kind and has an extremely special gift of reading ones body to see what needs to be done. He creates a really comforting and welcoming environment.

There’s so many more great things I could say.

I have recommended Walter to everyone I can because you get real results that can greatly improve your quality of life.
